commentTextItems.html: down the leg side, turned away to fine leg and the single takes India to victory!
another one! fuller and on the stumps, this time Dhoni picks up the long-on fence and clears it by a long long way, amazing hit
good length delivery outside the off stump and that's pounded over the long-off fence, Dhoni on the rampage now
short of a good length deivery outside the off stump, Dhoni swings across but fails to make contact
full down leg side, Yuvraj Singh flicks it away to deep square leg for an easy single
low fulltoss outside the off stump and Dhoni hammers it past the fielder at mid-on, massive over for India comes to an end

commentTextItems.html: full on the stumps, Dhoni drives it straight to the fielder at mid-on
Dhoni edges the ball
good line but too full, Dhoni drives on the on side
six more! under pressure Asif pitches it up outisde the off stump and Dhoni dismisses it over the long-off fence, India moving along nicely here
short of a length and close to the off stump line, Dhoni makes room and slices it away to the backward point fence, Asif under pressure straightaway
on the middle and leg stump line, played away through square leg and that's his fifty

commentTextItems.html: just short of a length, Yuvraj Singh cuts it away towards point and a wild throw at the bowler's end gives away four valuable runs!
driven down to long-on, easy single
good length delivery, Dhoni picks up the off-cutter and lofts it over the long-on fence, mighty six that
short delivery outside the off stump, ball keeps low and beats Dhoni
yorker on the pads, turned away to fine leg for a single
driven well wide of the fielder at cover, easy single and that's his 6th ODI hundred - excellent innings
